quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,137,"…óum wonaali si wanaa diina adinoo…ďe …ďen e naamuuji ma…ď…ďe e jikkuuji ma…ď…ďe."
  26,138,"Men wonaali leptoytee…ďe."
  26,139,"∆Āe jokki yiddugol Annabaajo ma…ď…ďe on Huudu (yo o his), Men halkiri …ďe henndu rimardu ndu sabu fennugol ma…ď…ďe ngol. pellet, wonii e ngol halkugol hangol tasakuyee wonannde taskotoo…ďe …ďen, …ďur…ďe heewude …ďen e ma…ď…ďe wonaali gom…óin…ďe."
  26,140,"Anndu Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo- ko Kanko woni teddu…óo Yo…ďtotoo…óo ay…ďe Makko …ďen Yurmetee…óo on tuubu…óo immorde e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  26,141,"Samuudinkoo…ďe …ďen finniino Nulaa…ďe …ďen sabu fennugol ma…ď…ďe Annabaajo ma…ď…ďe on Saalihu (yo o his)."
  26,142,"Tuma nde Saalihu musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on ka dammbe (asko) wi'annoo …ďe: Enee, on hulataa Alla, acciron rewugol tanaa Makko sabu kulol Makko?!"
  26,143,"Min, ko mi Nulaa…óo moo…óon, Alla Nulii lam e moo…óon, ko mi hoolaa…óo e nder ko mi yottinanta Mo kon, mi …ďeydataa e dow mu'un mi uytataa …óum kadi."
  26,144,"Huliree Alla …óoftagol Yamiraa…ói Makko …óin e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, …óoftee lam e ko mi yamiri on kon, e ko mi ha…ói on kon e muu…óum."
  26,145,"Mi …óa…ď…ďiraali on njo…ďdi fii ko mi yottinanta Joomi am kon e moo…óon, njo…ďdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Alla Jooma tageefooji …óin wanaa e tanaa Makko."
  26,146,"Enee, on tam∆īini nde accete…óon e nder koo ko wonu…óon e muu…óum immorde e mo∆ī∆īereeji e neemaaji ko on hoolii…ďe hara on hulaa?!"
  26,147,"E nder gese e can…ói ilooji."
  26,148,"E awruuji e tamarooje dim…óe majje …óen ko newii…óe …ďenndu…óe."
  26,149,"Hi…óon ta∆īa pelle …óen fii yo on wa…óu cuu…ói ho…óon e majji hara onon ko Ňčelir…ďe lesugol …ói."
  26,150,"Huliree Alla …óoftagol Yamiraa…ói Makko …óin e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaani Makko …óin, …óoftee lam e ko mi yamiri on kon, e ko mi ha…ói on kon e muu…óum."
  26,151,"Wata on …óowor yamaruyee fantiniroo…ďe …ďen e dow wonkiiji mu'un wa…ó…óitagol geddi …óin."
  26,152,"∆Āen bonniroo…ďe ka leydi sabu ko …ďe saakata kon immorde e geddi …óin, hara …ďe mo∆ī∆īinirtaa pittaali ma…ď…ďe jogitagol …óotaare Alla nden."
  26,153,"Yim…ďe makko …ďen wi'ani mo: Anndu, an ko a jeyaa…óo e …ďen mbil…óaa…ďe laawi …óuu…óu…ói, haa mbilewu ngun fooli hakkillaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin, ngu na…ďi …ói."
  26,154,"A wonaali si wanaa …ďanndunke wano amen alaa ko senndumaa e amen haa tawa a wonay Nulaa…óo, awa addii maande tinndinaynde wonndema an ko a Nulaa…óo, si tawii ko a goongu…óo e ko nodditi…óaa kon wonndema ko a Nulaa…óo."
  26,155,"Saalihu maakani …ďe -nde tawnoo Alla okkii mo maande nden, …óum le, ko ngelooba mba Alla yalti e nder fetere nden-: mbaa…óoo ko ngelooba himba yi'ee himba meemee, no woodani mba ge…ďal immorde e ndiyam …óam, onon kadi no woodani on ge…ďal anndaangal, mba yarataa e nden √Īalaande tawnde ko nde ge…ďal moo…óon, onon kadi wata on yaru dey e nden √Īalaande tawnde ko nde ge…ďal mabba."
  26,156,"Wata on memir mba ko lorrata mba immorde e borogogol maa…óum piyugol, sakko he…ďa on sabu …óum Lepte immorde ka Alla O halkira on …óe e nder √Īalaande mawnde sabu ko woni kon e mayre immorde albalaa'uuji jippotoo…ói e dow moo…óon."
  26,157,"∆Āe fottani boraade mba, …ďur…óo …ďe malkiseede on borii mba, …ďe wonti nimsu…ďe e dow ko …ďe huuwi kon nde …ďe anndunoo pellet, feere alaa Lepte …óen jippoto e ma…ď…ďe, kono nimse tuma yi'ugol Lepte …óen …óum nafataa."
  26,158,"Lepte …óe …ďe fodanoo …óen nanngi …ďe, …óen le; ko dillannde nden e haacaango ngon, pellet, wonii e koo ko jaŇčtaa…óoo immorde e fillayee fii Saalihu e yim…ďe makko …ďen tasakuyee wonannde taskotoo…ďe …ďen, …ďur…ďe heewude e ma…ď…ďe wonaali gom…óinoo…ďe"
  26,159,"Anndu Joomi maa…óa -an Nulaa…óo- ko Kanko woni teddu…óo Yo…ďtotoo…óo ay…ďe Makko …ďen, Yurmetee…óo on tuubu…óo immorde e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen."